<Trivia>[IMG]https://i.imgur.com/xQ1uaEd.png [/IMG]
Genesis Project is a multi platform demo group and one of the most well known and productive C64 cracking groups of all time, formed in late 1985 or early 1986 on the C64 by &amp;lt;scener id=6392&amp;gt; (TNT), later &amp;lt;scener id=315&amp;gt;. 

in 1993 a lot of the members strated cracking for SNES/PC etc. (See &amp;lt;release id=261018&amp;gt;. - SNES: L.A.Style, Tyger, Red Skin, Airwolf, Lexi, Zammbo. PC: Snacky)

A full detailed history 1986-2016 can be read in &amp;lt;release id=150629&amp;gt; (2016).

[url=https://demozoo.org/groups/3170/]The history of Genesis Project and further information.[/url]


Current (2024) G*P WHQ: &amp;lt;bbs id=103&amp;gt;, EHQ: &amp;lt;bbs id=1139&amp;gt;, and USHQ: &amp;lt;bbs id=320&amp;gt;. G*P also had
 &amp;lt;bbs id=114&amp;gt;, &amp;lt;bbs id=221&amp;gt;, &amp;lt;bbs id=42&amp;gt;, &amp;lt;bbs id=182&amp;gt;, &amp;lt;bbs id=113&amp;gt;, &amp;lt;bbs id=286&amp;gt;, &amp;lt;bbs id=39&amp;gt;, &amp;lt;bbs id=68&amp;gt; and &amp;lt;bbs id=218&amp;gt; as HQs.

G*P were the organizer of successful parties such as &amp;lt;event id=445&amp;gt;, &amp;lt;event id=128&amp;gt;, &amp;lt;event id=1846&amp;gt;, &amp;lt;event id=2316&amp;gt;, &amp;lt;event id=2879&amp;gt; and &amp;lt;event id=2756&amp;gt;.</Trivia>
